Nai.

624
00:22:57,320 --> 00:22:58,040
You try it.

625
00:22:58,040 --> 00:22:59,440
No.

626
00:22:59,440 --> 00:23:00,288
Just experience it.

627
00:23:00,288 --> 00:23:01,960
No.

628
00:23:01,960 --> 00:23:02,360
No.

629
00:23:02,360 --> 00:23:03,280
You have to try it.

630
00:23:04,880 --> 00:23:06,840
It tickles even if I do it to myself.

631
00:23:06,840 --> 00:23:07,640
You have to try it.

632
00:23:08,640 --> 00:23:12,736
