Who did I ever offend?

633
00:23:17,920 --> 00:23:18,520
Come on.

634
00:23:18,520 --> 00:23:20,608
- Why?
- Three, two, one.

635
00:23:25,560 --> 00:23:26,520
Doesn't it look like that sheep?

636
00:23:28,160 --> 00:23:29,360
Why?

637
00:23:32,240 --> 00:23:33,376
Why?

638
00:23:33,840 --> 00:23:35,240
